Troubleshooting Tips
Common Issues and Solutions
Issue 1: Tor Browser won't start

Solution: Check if the download completed successfully and verify file permissions:
ls -la /opt/tor-browser/Browser/start-tor-browser
chmod +x /opt/tor-browser/Browser/start-tor-browser
Issue 2: Proxychains not working

Solution: Verify Tor service is running and check configuration:
sudo systemctl status tor
sudo netstat -tlnp | grep 9050
Issue 3: DNS resolution issues

Solution: Reset DNS configuration:
sudo systemctl restart systemd-resolved
sudo systemctl flush-dns
Issue 4: Python tools not installing

Solution: Ensure virtual environment is activated and pip is updated:
source ~/osint-env/bin/activate
pip install --upgrade pip setuptools wheel
